Interface CustomTemplate

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
CustomTemplateImpl
public interface CustomTemplate
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Custom Template'. Un template custom da utilizzarsi per la generazione full del codice a fronte di un ExecCommand.

The following features are supported:

  • Tpl ID
  • Name
  • Model Slots

See Also:
GuigenPackage.getCustomTemplate()
